      Action taken before the state machine enters GPS.AppState.SEARCHING -> requests a new location by using the location_provider_.

      Action taken before the state machine enters GPS.AppState.ON -> dispatches a new GPSEvent.START event.
      private class  GPS.StopEntry
      Action taken before the state machine enter GPS.AppState.OFF -> destroy_internals() and dispatches a new GPSEvent.STOP.
